data.description: Location! Location! Location! Welcome to Sunrise Pointe Neighborhood in the desired SE Polk School District in Pleasant Hill. This 2 story home w/over 2,100sf of fin. has space for everyone. Main level features an open floor plan, living room area, pantry closet, & a nice sized laundry area. Dining area is near sliders to the very large deck which is right off of big FLAT backyard, that also includes a large storage shed in backyard. All appliances are included in the kitchen w/generous amount of cabinet & counter space. Bonus room (office, living room, dining room) & half bath finishes main level. Upstairs offers 4 bedrooms, 2 baths to include the master suite w/private bath & jetted tub. Stubbed and insulated basement ready for its next owners to finish, as well as a 3 car gar.
